headline: Digital Turbine Joins The Coalition for a Competitive Mobile Experience
summary: Digital Turbine, the leading platform powering premium mobile experiences through innovative technology, today announced its membership in The Coalition for a Competitive Mobile Experience (CCME). Digital Turbine joins founding members Garmin, Match Group, Meta, and Spotify to help advance the Coalition's mission of fostering a more open and competitive mobile app marketplace.
